<!-- Brand Story -->
<section class="about-hero section-padding bg-mint">
  <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
    <span class="label">Our Story</span>
    <h1>Built Out of Frustration with the Skincare Aisle</h1>
    <p class="about-hero__text">
      Nutrava started because skincare shopping is broken. The aisle is a lottery — a thousand bottles, each promising miracles, none designed with your actual skin in mind. Half the time you end up reacting, the other half you can't tell if anything's working.
    </p>
    <p class="about-hero__text" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      We're a small, founder-led brand. We built the quiz because we believe the right routine for you depends on your actual skin — your type, your concerns, your sensitivity, and what you already use. Every product in our catalog is one we'd use ourselves, at clinically meaningful percentages, with full INCI ingredient lists on every page.
    </p>
    <p class="about-hero__text" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      We're just getting started. No inflated customer counts, no fake reviews — just 12 formulas we stand behind, and a quiz that actually listens.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How Routines Work -->
<section class="about-section section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-xl">How Our Routines Work</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-card">
        <span class="about-card__icon"><i data-lucide="flask-conical"></i></span>
        <h3>Evidence-First Actives</h3>
        <p>Every formula is built around ingredients with clinical evidence — retinol, vitamin C, hyaluronic acid, peptides — at percentages that actually move the needle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <span class="about-card__icon"><i data-lucide="puzzle"></i></span>
        <h3>Designed to Layer</h3>
        <p>Your routine isn't four random products — it's a cleanser, serum, and moisturiser chosen to work together. We handle the order and the balance so you don't have to.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <span class="about-card__icon"><i data-lucide="target"></i></span>
        <h3>Matched to Your Skin</h3>
        <p>Acne-prone, mature, dehydrated, sensitive — every skin tells a different story. Your routine is matched to yours, not to a generic bestseller shelf.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Promise -->
<section class="about-section section-padding">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-xl">Our Promise</h2>
    <div class="about-promises">
      <div class="about-promise">
        <span class="trust-badge__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Clean Formulas</h4>
          <p>No synthetic fragrance, no sulphates, no mystery proprietary blends. Just the ingredients that earn a spot on the label.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-promise">
        <span class="trust-badge__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Clinically Meaningful Percentages</h4>
          <p>Vitamin C at levels that brighten. Retinol at levels that work. Hyaluronic acid in four weights, not a decorative drop. No pixie dust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-promise">
        <span class="trust-badge__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Transparent Ingredients</h4>
          <p>Full INCI lists on every product. Nothing hidden. If something is in there, we tell you — and tell you why.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-promise">
        <span class="trust-badge__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Cruelty-Free, Always</h4>
          <p>Never tested on animals. Most of our range is vegan too — each product page lists the details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="about-section section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="about-faq">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">How does the personalised quiz work?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">The quiz takes under 60 seconds. It asks about your skin type, top concern, current routine, SPF habits, and any history of reactions. Based on your answers, we match you with a 2–4 product routine — Essential, Recommended, or Complete.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Can I buy individual products instead of a full routine?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. The quiz results page shows each product individually with its own add-to-cart button. Routines are just a curated shortcut — nothing is gated behind them.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">How long until I see results?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Hydrating and calming products usually feel different on day one. Brightening and anti-aging actives take 2–4 weeks to show visible changes, with full benefits building over 6–8 weeks of consistent use.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Are your products safe for sensitive skin?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Several of our formulas are built specifically for reactive skin — fragrance-free, acid-free, and free of common irritants. The quiz flags products that suit sensitive skin. Always patch test before first use, and consult a dermatologist for severe skin conditions.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">What's your shipping and returns policy?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Free US shipping on orders over $50. Orders typically arrive in 3–5 business days. Every product is covered by our 30-day money-back guarantee — if it doesn't work for your skin, we refund you, no questions asked.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Quiz CTA -->
{% section 'quiz-cta' %}

